<plot>It was just a regular "ladies' night"-or at least it was supposed to be. The next morning a handsome foreigner is found dead in the quarry behind a rural New Jersey home. Was it murder? An accident? A drunken orgy gone wrong? Three smalltown cops put the pieces together from the very different recollections of the women involved.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?584861</url></doc>
